PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1781959682
OL,3,CCompensation for pupils given infected
OL,4,Cblood 'nowhere near enough', says MP
OL,6,FThe Lord Mayor Treloar College in
OL,7,FHampshire offered specialist care for
OL,8,Fchildren with haemophilia during the
OL,9,F1970s and 1980s. Pupils undergoing
OL,10,Ftreatment for the disorder were
OL,11,Fexperimented on without their
OL,12,Fknowledge by clinicians.
OL,14,FCabinet Office minister Nick Thomas-
OL,15,FSymonds increased the compensation
OL,16,Fpayments for the former students from
OL,17,F#25,000 to #60,000, earlier this year.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1781959682
OL,3,CCompensation for pupils given infected
OL,4,Cblood 'nowhere near enough', says MP
OL,6,FMore than 30,000 people in the UK were
OL,7,Finfected with HIV and hepatitis C
OL,8,Fafter they were given contaminated
OL,9,Fblood and blood products between the
OL,10,F1970s and early 1990s.
OL,12,FMore than 3,000 people have died as a
OL,13,Fresult while survivors are living with
OL,14,Flifelong health implications.
OL,16,FMr Thomas-Symonds said the
OL,17,Fcompensation "must reflect and embody"
OL,18,Finfected patients' experiences "if it
OL,19,Fis to truly deliver justice" when
OL,20,Fannouncing the increase in April.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1781959682
OL,3,CCompensation for pupils given infected
OL,4,Cblood 'nowhere near enough', says MP
OL,6,FLeading a debate on the infected blood
OL,7,Fcompensation scheme on Thursday, Mr
OL,8,FEfford urged ministers to withdraw the
OL,9,Foffer.
OL,11,FHe said: "These children, without
OL,12,Ftheir knowledge, were given
OL,13,Fcontaminated products, so that their
OL,14,Feffects could be studied by the state
OL,15,Fthat should have been there to protect
OL,16,Fthem.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1781959682
OL,3,CCompensation for pupils given infected
OL,4,Cblood 'nowhere near enough', says MP
OL,6,F"Imagine being one of the victims,
OL,7,Freflecting on what the state has done
OL,8,Fto you, knowing your life has been
OL,9,Faltered, shortened, friends you have
OL,10,Flost."
OL,12,FMr Efford added: "I spoke to one
OL,13,Fparent who's described to me, looking
OL,14,Fat her three children, knowing she
OL,15,Fwould never see them grow up to be
OL,16,Fadults, not see them married, never
OL,17,Fsee her grandchildren.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1781959682
OL,3,CCompensation for pupils given infected
OL,4,Cblood 'nowhere near enough', says MP
OL,6,F"The top price for that is #60,000. If
OL,7,Fyou're a pharmaceutical company, come
OL,8,Fto Britain, we set the price low
OL,9,Fenough that you can carry out
OL,10,Fexperiments on everyone, and then you
OL,11,Fcan pay the fine and still make money.
OL,13,F"It is priceless what these people
OL,14,Fhave lost, #60,000 is nowhere near
OL,15,Fenough. It's not just the size of the
OL,16,Fcompensation, but the gravity of what
OL,17,Ftook place, and the immorality of it,
OL,18,Fand this has to be addressed, and
OL,19,Fthese payments go nowhere near it."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1781959682
OL,3,CCompensation for pupils given infected
OL,4,Cblood 'nowhere near enough', says MP
OL,6,FMr Efford acknowledged the rise from
OL,7,F#25,000 to #60,000 was a "welcome step
OL,8,Fin the right direction", but pressed
OL,9,Ffor a timescale for distributing
OL,10,Fcompensation.
OL,12,FResponding to the debate, Mr Thomas-
OL,13,FSymonds said #2.7 billion worth of
OL,14,Foffers have been made, and #2.1
OL,15,Fbillion has been paid in compensation.
OL,17,FHe added: "I do not think there is any
OL,18,Famount of money that could ever make
OL,19,Fup for the experimentation on children
OL,20,Fthat happened as a consequence of this
OL,21,Fscandal."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1781959682
OL,3,CCompensation for pupils given infected
OL,4,Cblood 'nowhere near enough', says MP
OL,6,FHe also said he was "troubled" by the
OL,7,Flevel of evidence being required of
OL,8,Ffamilies to claim compensation.
OL,10,F"This is often an ask for evidence of
OL,11,Fthings that happened a long time ago,
OL,12,Fbut secondly, what we also know from
OL,13,FSir Brian Langstaff's inquiry is there
OL,14,Fwas deliberate document destruction,"
OL,15,Fhe said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1781959682
OL,3,CCompensation for pupils given infected
OL,4,Cblood 'nowhere near enough', says MP
OL,6,F"For those two reasons, I have
OL,7,Frepeatedly said from the despatch box
OL,8,Fthat I expect not just a sympathetic
OL,9,Fapproach to evidence, but also some
OL,10,Fassistance, some pointers as to where
OL,11,Fevidence is required, where it might
OL,12,Fbe able to be obtained."
OL,14,FThe Cabinet Office minister said they
OL,15,Fhad recently held a public
OL,16,Fconsultation asking for feedback on
OL,17,Fthe scheme, and a full set of
OL,18,Fregulations to make legislative
OL,19,Fchanges will be brought to the House
OL,20,F"shortly".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1781959682
OL,3,CCompensation for pupils given infected
OL,4,Cblood 'nowhere near enough', says MP
OL,6,FHe also said the Hillsborough Law,
OL,7,Fwhich would create a statutory duty
OL,8,Ffor public authorities to tell the
OL,9,Ftruth, was "well over 90% of the way
OL,10,Fthere".
OL,12,F"The outstanding issue on the
OL,13,FHillsborough law is how exactly we
OL,14,Fstrike that balance between the duty
OL,15,Fof candour and the work of the
OL,16,Fsecurity and intelligence services,
OL,17,Fbut I am very confident that we can
OL,18,Fresolve that satisfactorily," he said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
